    @**** ModRapidGate ****@
    <h2 id="mod-rapid-gate">Rapid Gate</h2>
    <div>ModRapidGate 6.0.0.0 (In development)</div>
    <ul>
        <li>Implemented the mode of automatic download of an archive from a backup server</li>
        <li>Events are transferred when replicating archives</li>
        <li>Event acknowledgments are transferred</li>
        <li>Added an option to replicate only by command</li>
        <li>Archive mask for receiving and transmitting</li>
        <li>Option whether to apply formulas and generate events on data transfer</li>
        <li>Server address is checked to prevent loops</li>
        <li>Gateways are controlled by command code without using channel number</li>
        <li>Module task queue</li>
    </ul>

